      <p>
        Harder Labs LLC is a Texas limited liability company based in Austin, Texas. We operate
        multiple brands and services under official DBA (doing business as) filings, including but
        not limited to:
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li>Hill Country Gear (hillcountrygear.com)</li>
        <li>Stellar Arcade (stellararcade.com)</li>
        <li>SharePuzzles (sharepuzzles.com)</li>
