      <p>You agree not to:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Use our Services for any unlawful purpose</li>
        <li>Interfere with or disrupt the operation of our Services</li>
        <li>Attempt to gain unauthorized access to any part of our Services</li>
        <li>Scrape, harvest, or collect information from our Services without permission</li>
        <li>Use automated systems (bots, crawlers) to access our Services in a manner that sends
            more requests than a human could reasonably produce</li>
        <li>Impersonate any person or entity</li>
